tYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA0MTUmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW=
1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa878ae02" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" ite=
mscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">without Neumann=E2=
=80=99s patter</a> (that may not actually be the reason), and Neumann start=
ed talking about maybe <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/35042113.285343/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMjMtMTEtMDkvYWRhbS1uZXVtYW5uLWlzLXNvLWdvb2QtYXQtdGhpcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwN=
